name: Antique Kundan Mangtikkas
long_desc:
•Sri Shringarr Fashion Traditional Micro Gold Polished Semi Precious Kundan Mangtikka designed by Yosshita & Neha. 
•Look feminine and elegant by wearing these beautiful mangtikka.
•Featuring attractive designs, these earrings can look elegant and stylish when worn with anarkali, lehengas, gowns or sarees. 
•So enhance your style quotient on almost any occasion by wearing these mangtikka.
•It has Copper metal base. 
•Give a rich yet elegant touch to your attire.  
•This mangtikka have been intricately designed for all the jewellery lovers.
